  "client_id": "...",
  "client_secret": "...",
  "authorize_url": "...",
  "token_url": "..."
}
```

✅ **CORRECT - Platform 3.0 format:**
```json
{
  "integrations": {
    "oauth_name": {
      "display_name": "Service Name",
      "client_id": "{{client_id}}",
      "client_secret": "{{client_secret}}",
      "authorize_url": "https://...",
      "token_url": "https://...",
      "token_type": "account",
      "options": {
        "scope": "read"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

**OAuth Request Template:**

Must include:
1. `options.oauth` with OAuth config name
2. `Authorization` header with `<%= access_token %>`

```json
{
  "myOAuthRequest": {
    "schema": {
      "method": "GET",
      "host": "api.example.com",
      "path": "/resource",
      "headers": {
        "Authorization": "bearer <%= access_token %>"
      }
    },
    "options": {
      "oauth": "oauth_name"
    }
  }
}
```

